metadata.name: Cosplay Club #2
metadata.description:
Cosplay Club is a community of cosplay enthusiast, artists, and musicians who love to create, share, and celebrate the art of cosplay.

There are 3333 different Cosplay Club NFTs to collect, each one featuring original artwork by our talented artist.

Our composer has also created 15 original songs which will be unlockable for owners of the NFTs.
